# @guebbit/react-toolkit

React + Zustand toolkit ported from `@guebbit/vue-toolkit`.

## Install

```bash
npm i @guebbit/react-toolkit react zustand zod
```

## Exports

- `useCoreStore` (Zustand)
- `useNotificationsStore` (Zustand)
- `useStructureDataManagement`
- `useStructureRestApi`
- `useStructureFormValidation`

## Vue -> React mapping

- Vue composables -> toolkit hooks (`use*`)
- Pinia stores -> Zustand stores
- `ref/computed` values are exposed via `.value` compatibility refs

## Examples

### Hook

```ts
const users = useStructureDataManagement<{ id: number; name: string }>('id');
users.addRecord({ id: 1, name: 'Ada' });
console.log(users.itemList.value);
```

### Zustand store

```ts
const notifications = useNotificationsStore.getState();
notifications.addMessage('Saved');
console.log(notifications.messages());
```
